{"tid":1071654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"當我見到李慧詩⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-03-21T13:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T16:19:42.000Z","uid":60344,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31bfecaf42eb527020070b4d1adb47c5dea92f1e","tid":1071654,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"我真係驕傲香港有個咁開朗的運動員！<br />\n<br />\n外表冇人地咁好<br />\n新聞自然集中佢的運動表現<br />\n佢在新聞出現<br />\n唔係賣化妝品廣告<br />\n唔係賣女性用品廣告<br />\n而係奪得世界賽金牌<br />\n代表香港攞彩虹戰衣<br />\n<br />\n我唔識單車<br />\n但當年王金寶條片我都有睇過<br />\n感動由心而發<br />\n再睇李慧詩攞獎後訪問<br />\n台上台下都有大家姐的開朗笑容<br />\n我唔識佢<br />\n但印象好好<br />\n<br />\n李慧詩，多謝你，香港有你係福氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4177f9d5dd934cb065b451a856bd4352d42728","tid":1071654,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaedfc0f650cd7a97000d7817156ab051739b6b","tid":1071654,"uid":124277,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果佢靚d 你慌佢唔拍"},{"pid":"4d24cd4df9f92414d10f48c054910fae32394219","tid":1071654,"uid":60344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59410766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59410766&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3C%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=63b00127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59410766&h=c5cf608d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190326/59410766</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gi